column2: SELECT m.iauname AS iauname, m.ra AS ra_gz, m.dec AS dec_gz, o.objid AS dr7objid_sdss, o.ra AS ra_sdss, o.dec AS dec_sdss, o.petroMag_g, o.petroMag_r, o.z AS z_sdss, p.fracDeV_r, p.deVAB_r, p.petroRad_r into mydb.GZ_DECALS_# from MyDB.GZ_DECALS_#_coor AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objID LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p on n.objid = p.objID
